              },
              "free_text": [
                " The uncertainty of the energy was estimated",
                "from the following components: energy of the primary",
                "incident beam and target thickness taking into account",
                "the well known energy straggling effect."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " For estimation of the uncertainties of the",
                "cross-sections, the linearly contributing processes",
                "were taken into account with equal sensitivities.",
                "The errors of nonlinear parameters (time, etc.) were",
                "not considered but their contribution is negligible",
                "compared to the linear parameters.",
                "The typical cross-section uncertainty was around +-16%"
              ]
            }
